blog.title: maledettadaunangelo
blog.description:
A volte devi indietreggiare di uno o due passi, riconsiderare, staccare per un mese. Non fare niente, non volere niente. La pace è fondamentale, il ritmo è fondamentale. Qualsiasi cosa tu voglia non l'avrai mai provandoci con troppa insistenza.
— Charles Bukowski

summary: In a fate where you are doomed to be abandoned and prosecuted for no fault of your own (i.e. solomon ending w the interrogation...
body:
In a fate where you are doomed to be abandoned and prosecuted for no fault of your own (i.e. solomon ending w the interrogation and loss of friends), no servant will defend and protect you as viciously as an avenger class

They are a massive comfort because their entire existence is what you are destined to experience, and as the class of bloody teeth and vengeful howls they would love nothing more than to break destiny and Finally Succeed in protecting what they love
